*gaim-0.5.7 (29 Dec 2002)

  29 Dec 2002; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@gentoo.org>: updated to latest version
  of gaim, reworked deps to make them simpler, cleaned up the build code, and
  allowed gtk+ and glib version 2.2.x to satisfy their respective deps (closing
  bug 12641.) Unmasked for the 1.4 release for x86, ~ for ppc.

  23 Dec 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> :
  Fix glib and gtk+ deps, as it seems to work with versions 2.2.0 ...

