*gaim-0.59-r3 (18 Aug 2002)

  18 Aug 2002; Bruce A. Locke <blocke@shivan.org> gaim-0.59-r3.ebuild:

*gaim-0.59-r3 (18 Aug 2002)

  18 Aug 2002; Bruce A. Locke <blocke@shivan.org> gaim-0.59-r3.ebuild:

  Support for the optional "gtk2" keyword added to ebuild.  Gaim can
  now be built in one of the three following configurations:

  - gtk+ 1.2 version only
  - gtk+ 1.2 version with gnome 1.4 applet
  - gtk+ 2.0 version only

